description: This file defines a mock class for the IWarehouse interface, used for testing purposes. It includes mock methods for warehouse operations such as registration, hardware testing, reset, and cleanup, as well as a notification class mock.

classes.name: WarehouseMock
classes.description: A mock implementation of the IWarehouse interface for unit testing.

classes.name: WarehouseNotificationMock
classes.description: A mock implementation of the IWarehouse::INotification interface for testing notifications.

methods.name: Register
methods.description: Mocks the registration of a notification callback.

methods.name: Unregister
methods.description: Mocks the unregistration of a notification callback.

methods.name: InternalReset
methods.description: Mocks resetting the warehouse with a passphrase.

methods.name: IsClean
methods.description: Mocks checking if the device is clean based on age.

methods.name: ResetDevice
methods.description: Mocks resetting the device with optional reboot.

methods.name: ResetDone
methods.description: Mocks notification callback for reset completion.
